column7: This large ancient lake straddling the border between Albania & Macedonia reaches a depth of 300m.
Lake bordered by mountains popular for fishing boating & views of a partially submerged church.
Picturesque freshwater lake bordered by national parkland offering trails & abundant flora & fauna.
Picturesque lake bordered by national parkland featuring trails alongside abundant flora & fauna.
